subject: Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 285, Saskatchewan
precis: Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 285 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Saskatchewan with respect to the interface fires that occurred from August 9 to September 23, 2024.
